## Requirements

- Python 3.12+{% if docker %} / Docker{% endif %}

## Setup

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
cp .env.example .env
```
{% if use_db %}
Edit `.env` and set `DATABASE_URL` before running.

```bash
alembic upgrade head
```
{% endif %}

## Running

```bash
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

- API: `http://localhost:8000`
- Docs: `http://localhost:8000/docs`
